<emphasis id="B970EAFEFFE7F6098BFC359AFCD8FE3C" bold="true" box="[738,893,390,423]" pageId="35" pageNumber="93">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
Cynonycleris 
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFE7F6098D27359AFCD4FE54" authority="Bocage, 1889" authorityName="Bocage" authorityYear="1889" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Myonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="93" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="brachycephala">brachycephala Bocage, 1889</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation id="3B6C3CB1FFE7F6098A9735B5FC3BFE6D" pageId="35" pageNumber="93">
<collectingCountry id="F313767CFFE7F6098A9735B5FB21FE54" box="[905,1156,425,463]" name="Sao Tome Island" pageId="35" pageNumber="93">Sao Tomé Island</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F313767CFFE7F6098D8335B5FC3FFE6D" name="Sao Tome and Principe" pageId="35" pageNumber="93">Sao Tomé and Principe</collectingCountry>
.
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBB36ECFFE7F6098BFD35E0FBA7FD21" blockId="35.[738,1330,390,817]" pageId="35" pageNumber="93">
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFE7F6098BFD35E0FB90FD86" authorityName="Bocage" authorityYear="1889" box="[739,1077,508,541]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Myonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="93" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="brachycephala">Myonycteris brachycephala</taxonomicName>
is closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFE7F6098A12363FFC0CFDDF" authorityName="Dobson" authorityYear="1878" box="[780,937,547,580]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Myonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="93" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="torquata">M. torquata</taxonomicName>
(separation occurred c.1-8 million years ago); it was placed in a separate subgenus (Phygetis), which has been rejected. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C31E6567FFE7F6098BFC36DDFC72FC91" pageId="35" pageNumber="93" type="distribution">
